These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, aristoff, ritmeester, bolivar, swisher, dannemann, montecristo
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: march, april, july, february, november, june, january
 1. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is the bolivar-smoker##1
 3. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 5. the ritmeester-smoker is in the middle##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
 7. the swisher-smoker is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 8. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
10. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
11. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Cigar           | swisher | bolivar | aristoff | ritmeester | siglo | dannemann | montecristo |
| Birthday   | march    | november   | february      | june | july    | april    | january         |

