.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: indonesian, mexican, nigerian, thai, colombian, polish, australian
7 different pets are kept: lizard, bird, hamster, cat, goat, horse, chinchilla
 1. the owner of the goat is the thai##1
 2. the polish is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 3. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
 4. the mexican is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 5. the thai is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 6. the polish is on the left of the australian##1
 7. the owner of the goat is in the middle##1
 8. the owner of the goat is on the right of the colombian##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the nigerian##1
10. the thai is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Nationality          | indonesian | mexican | colombian | thai | polish | australian | nigerian |
| Pet   | bird      | hamster   | cat   | goat      | lizard       | chinchilla       | horse     |

