 3. the polish is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 4. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the palace house##1
 5. the pakistani is the tower house##1
 6. the dutch is on the right of the polish##1
 7. the polish is on the left of the dutch##1
 8. the polish is on the right of the brazilian##1
 9. the palace house is the brazilian##1
10. the victorian house is on the right of the pakistani##1
11. the brazilian is in the middle##1
12. the art-deco house is on the left of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| House   | farmhouse | tower     | victorian  | palace       | gothic-revival       | art-deco  | colonial   |
| Nationality    | argentine  | pakistani | malaysian | brazilian | polish | dutch | nigerian |

