.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, tea, coffee, water, lemonade, juice
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: classical, r&b, folk, blues, jazz, ambient, electronic
 1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
 2. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 3. the person drinking juice is the fan of blues##1
 4. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 6. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 7. the fan of classical is the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person drinking water is in the middle##1
 9. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
10. the fan of classical is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate  | juice | coffee | water | lemonade     | iced-tea | tea |
| Music-Genre     | ambient | blues      | electronic | folk    | jazz | r&b   | classical  |

