 3. the person watching drama movies is the person who growstulip##1
 4. the person who growstulip is on the far left##1
 5. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
 6. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who growsdaisy##1
 7. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 8. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the person watching scientific movies is in the middle##1
10. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |       4       |     5      |     6      |    7    |
